spell_2382r2jk.description: Freezes the target car and makes them slide

spell_hg6ddry4.description: Meteors hit the target car causing a demolition on the 3rd hit

spell_kdh7hy7r.description: The car is able to pass through other cars and is invisible and cannot be targeted by spells

spell_1h69nt0e.description: The car starts zapping other cars around it, slowing them down for a few seconds

spell_cez3dcf4.description: Surrounds the car with floating plasma blades which circle the player that uses the spells car for 6 seconds. Any car that enters melee range is instantly demo'd.

spell_11pe1m2e.description: Channels powerful red telekinesis to lift all nearby enemy cars into the air. For 3 seconds, they float helplessly around the caster, before being slammed to the ground in a devastating magical explosion (a demolition)

spell_cd3res63.description: Shoots a fireball at the target

spell_th5ek2kw.description: Summons a magical war hammer that autonomously flies around the track at high speed, seeking out enemy cars and zapping them with lightning as it passes.

spell_vcqct6hp.description: The car is able to have unlimited nitros for a period of time

spell_f74x59gz.description: Summons 5 illusionary clones of the user (slightly invisible) car that follow their movement. They block targeting from single target spells and explode if they touch other players causing them to demo. They can pick up spells, boosts, coins and shields. If the clones touch the wall or barrier they also explode.

spell_2dg5get6.description: Exchanges players car position with the targeted opponoents car position (targets the player in front).

spell_0tk74qn8.description: Emits a screech that disables boosts and spells of everyone in the map for a period of time.

spell_mmt7v0j0.description: The car produces a supersonic blast around it and demolishes other cars around it

spell_zdgrp9zk.description: Lazer beam blasts player one, stunning them for a period of time

spell_3tgjmyqv.description: Turns the car into a jet for some time

spell_pbvvrhw7.description: Shrinks down the car and the car is able to demo other cars
